  "text": "[14] More importantly, we draw the reader's attention to the 27-year segments highlighted in blue: Over these periods, the model trends are equal to +0.127 10 6 km 2 , the observed value reported by [CITATION_1] for the 1979-2005 period. What is clear from Figure 2 is that the trends of this magnitude appear spontaneously, in all four models, in the absence of any external forcing, anthropogenic or otherwise.",
